decks.notes: This deck focuses on utilizing a wide range of low-cost and efficient creatures and artifacts to quickly build up a powerful board presence and overwhelm the opponent with aggressive plays. By combining mana acceleration cards like Utopia Sprawl and Birds of Paradise with threats like Questing Beast and Walking Ballista, the deck aims to put pressure on the opponent from the very start of the game. Additionally, cards like Berserk and Ram Through provide extra burst damage potential to finish off opponents quickly. The inclusion of cards like Gaea's Touch and Sylvan Library help to ensure a steady stream of resources to maintain the aggression throughout the game.
